      "start": "09:30",
      "duration": "03:30",
      "abstract": "**[Registration](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Commons_Photographers_User_Group/Wikimania_2026_Pre-Conference)**\r\n\r\nThe Commons Photographers User Group organizes a pre-conference for the members of the user group and all people interested in photography and Wikimedia Commons.\r\n\r\n# **Schedule:**\r\n\r\n**[See the full schulde here.](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Commons:Commons_Photographers_User_Group/Wikimania_2026_Pre-Conference)**\r\n\r\n|  |  |\r\n| --- | --- |\r\n| 09:30-09:35 | **Welcome** |\r\n| 09:35-10:00 | **Introduction to the Commons Photographers User Group** - [Frank Schulenburg](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Frank_Schulenburg \"User:Frank Schulenburg\") |\r\n| 10:00-10:30 | **Tools for media navigation** - [Fuzheado](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Fuzheado \"User:Fuzheado\") |\r\n| 10:30-13:00 | **Find a common vision for Wikimedia Commons** |\r\n| 13:00-13:05 | **Group photo** |\r\n| 13:05-14:30 | **Lunch break** |\r\n| **14:30-18:45** | **Photographers and Commons project showcase** |\r\n| 14:30-15:00 | **Plan successful photography trips** - [Frank Schulenburg](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Frank_Schulenburg \"User:Frank Schulenburg\") & [Matthias Süßen](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Matthias_S%C3%BC%C3%9Fen \"User:Matthias Süßen\") |\r\n| 15:00-15:30 | **Trip to Southern India** - [Wuselig](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Wuselig \"User:Wuselig\") |\r\n| 15:30-16:00 | **Tools that make Wikimedia Commons contribution reliable and easy** - [Suyash.dwivedi](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Suyash.dwivedi \"User:Suyash.dwivedi\") |\r\n| 16:00-16:30 | **Sports photography on Wikimedia Commons** - [Stepro](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Stepro \"User:Stepro\") |\r\n| 16:30-16:45 | **Short break** |\r\n| 16:45-17:15 | **New Upload tools for structured data** - [Seewolf](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Seewolf \"User:Seewolf\") |\r\n| 17:15-17:45 | **Using GIS and Maps for Wiki takes events** - [Ailura](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Ailura \"User:Ailura\") |\r\n| 17:45-18:15 | **Ulli Beier’s photography and its role in preserving cultural heritage** - [Tunde Akangbe](https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:Tunde_Akangbe&action=edit&redlink=1) |\r\n| 18:15-18:45 | **Geography game/app in Basque (Tagzania)** - [Luistxo](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Luistxo \"User:Luistxo\") |\r\n| 18:45-19:00 | **Closing and introduction of open end practical photography skill share** |\r\n| 19:00-Open end | **Practical photography skill share/Photowalk** |",
