      "abstract": "Welcome to Wikimania 2026! The opening ceremony will be a dynamic, jam-packed event that celebrates both Freedom, Reliability and Equity as well as Wikipedia's 25th year as its central themes. The ceremony will include:\r\n\r\n* An opening video\r\n* A brief welcome from the Wikimania Steering Committee\r\n* Welcomes from the Core Organizing Team\r\n* Entertainment\r\n* Reflections from Bernadette Meehan, the Wikimedia Foundation CEO, on her journey [Around the puzzle globe](https://wikimedia.eventyay.com/redirect/?url=https%3A//meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Foundation/Chief_Executive_Officer/Around_the_puzzle_globe/en%3AZV5e1lFBfPQsctIA_noa85diZsMEFh6JGv4WOcA3vIg)\r\n* Wikimedian of the Year awards ceremony",
