      "abstract": "Workshop for developing a vision and a strategy for Wikimedians in Residence, hosted by members of the Wikimedians in Residence Exchange Network, and open to all interested in supporting and developing this particular outreach approach. Will feature several breakout sessions to explore the challenges and opportunities regarding the role and its future, including interactions with AI, funding and partnership models, prioritizing and building needed software features, and joint actions and guidelines for people acting as Wikimedians in Residence across various contexts.",
