      "abstract": "The Melange is a meetup for everyone that works with cultural and heritage in the WIkimedia Movement.\r\n\r\nPlease [register for this Meetup via Meta-wiki](https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Event:M%C3%A9lange_%E2%80%94_A_Content_Partnerships_Hub,_GLAM,_WiR,_Lib,_Culture_and_Heritage_Meetup) so we can contact you and follow up afterwards. Here we will also keep the **agenda up to date**, and you can leave **comments on the talk page** in advance of the meetup.",
