          "name": "Manfred Werner (WMAT) / Tsui",
          "bio": "From Vienna, Austria. As User:Tsui I am a writing Wikipedian since 2004, then became contributor to Wikimedia Commons since its beginning. In the meantime I also participate in Wikidata and other projects here and there. Since 2018 I am an employee at Wikimedia Austria, mostly working on community projects, supporting people who dedicate their time and contribute their knowledge and media to Wikimedia projects. Part of my time there is dedicated to supporting the organising team of Wiki Loves Monuments.\r\nOverall I have participated in, then also organised and supported quite a lot of contests, from writing, to Wikidata and most of all photography, both national and international.",
          "url": "https://wikimedia.eventyay.com/wm/wikimania2026/speakers/X799ZM/"
