      "start": "16:00",
      "duration": "01:25",
      "abstract": "This workshop demonstrates how to go **from idea to working, deployed tool in under two hours**, using Agentic AI (Claude Code).\r\n\r\nThe workshop is aimed at **people with programming experience**, to encourage them to experiment with agentic AI coding (which has made a great leap in capability in Nov 2025, and became much better at producing useful code). It is **not** aimed at encouraging people with **no understanding of programming** to \"just vibe code\".\r\n\r\nThe goal is to generate the idea for the tool right there in the room in the first 10 minutes or so, but I will also prepare a couple of ideas of my own in case there's no creative energy in the room.",
