      "language": "en",
      "room": "Room 3",
      "day": "2026-07-24",
      "start": "11:00",
      "duration": "00:55",
      "abstract": "By the time of Wikimania 2026 in Paris, the pilot on the ecosystem of movement organizations will reach its essential milestone of presenting clear proposal for the future landscape of movement organizations. The session will create the opportunity for the participants to hear about the details of the proposal, to then discuss it in the workshop format to clarify any aspects and fully understand the impact to their affiliate and the community. The pilot will move on to experimentation, where any feedback and suggestions improvement from the session will be integrated.",
