      "day": "2026-07-25",
      "start": "13:30",
      "duration": "01:00",
      "abstract": "Have you ever played a [Wikidata game](https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Wikidata:Games)? How about [listening to Wikipedia](https://listen.hatnote.com/)? Have you been making, or wanting to make, your own wiki games or interactive art? This meetup is for you!\r\n\r\nWe are bringing together creative technologists, game makers, and enthusiasts of the above to discuss all thing Wiki and games. It could be games to interact with knowledge; games for Wikipedia and GLAM partners; games to encourage adding content to Wiki projects; interactive installations and everything in between. The meetup is intended to connect people with these shared interests across the movement and bounce off ideas!",
