      "abstract": "The Wikimedia Conference and Events portfolio is instrumental in supporting and shaping up the way our community meets, sustains engagement and collaborates across the globe. Through this workshop we aim to bring together past, present and future conference organizers to share learnings, lessons and best practices while also providing feedback for the continuous improvement and effectiveness of the portfolio. The session will also create space to reflect on how we design events with clear purpose, strong outcomes, and equitable access.",
