          "bio": "I work with as a Manager (Global Events & South Asia) with the Movement Communications Team (WMF), which aims to build connections, help people understand the Wikimedia mission and celebrate their role in its success. \r\nCurrently, I serve as the Regional Specialist for South Asia, I work on the Core team for Wikimania, and am leading the Conference and Events portfolio. In the recent past, I have provided strategic support to various convening and conferences like WikiConference India, ESEAP Conference, WikiWomen’s Camp, Wikimedia Technology Summit etc.",
