          "bio": "My name is Mattia L. Nappi, I sign as sNappy. Since 2025 I am part of Wikimedia Italia Board. I am an engineer, I am very keen on project management, best practices improval, creative approach.\r\n\r\nI especially follow the field of advocacy and volunteers growth.",
