      "abstract": "This meetup brings together contributors and organisers of Wiki Loves Folklore and Feminism and Folklore to share experiences, challenges, and ideas for documenting intangible cultural heritage and women’s cultural knowledge on Wikimedia projects. The session will focus on collaboration, practical solutions, and building cross-community connections.",
