      "abstract": "The following Lightning talks will be showcased:\r\n\r\n1. [Wiki Loves Maps Mentorship Program](https://wikimedia.eventyay.com/wm/wikimania2026/talk/review/QNRVXBXDU8NWEQAHKPYTXXGBELEYTAAY) by Akouete\r\n2. [Wikipedia Editing as a Mental Health Practice](https://wikimedia.eventyay.com/wm/wikimania2026/talk/review/MF9TGXADCNCKMVCEETEAZEGMGPZ7UDYW) by Kate Kifa",
