      "start": "14:30",
      "duration": "00:55",
      "abstract": "**The full-scale war in Ukraine has radically changed the life of the wiki community, but at the same time it has become a catalyst for women's solidarity. In our presentation, we will talk about how Ukrainian female Wikipedians and educators — despite shelling, blackouts, and forced displacement — not only continue their volunteer work on Wikipedia, but also create sustainable networks of mutual support.**",
