      "abstract": "Abstract Wikipedia is now the newest Wikimedia project, having launched earlier this year. We will show you how you can create an abstract article on the site, powered by Wikidata and Wikifunctions, and see it previewed in multiple languages. We will demonstrate how you can use this today on Abstract Wikipedia. We will showcase where you can help build up data about your topics on Wikidata, and words and builders for your language on Wikidata Lexemes and Wikifunctions. We will highlight how you might be able to use this in future on your local Wikipedia.",
